thread.title: BRETT
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by BRETT

author: BRETT
title: BRETT
text: Booked really early and got a great price. The web based linked insurance policy was fair although not needed. Vehicle was ready to go and the size type I was expecting. It was in great condition and immaculate. Service was personable, friendly and helpful. Would definately use this company in Australia again.
